# Graceful degradation

| Service | If missing / fails |
|---------|-------------------|
| `GEMINI_API_KEY` | Text PDF: heuristic parse only; no hard crash. Image PDF: manual continue (heuristics need text). |
| Gemini 503 / high demand | Retry with backoff; fall back to heuristics on text PDFs; image PDF → friendly error + **Continue manually** |
| `RESEND_API_KEY` | Skip confirmation email; log server-side; intake still completes |
| Parse failure | Stay on upload step; manual continue |
| Supabase misconfig | Clear 500 / module warn at startup |

Do not block core intake → DOCX path on optional integrations. Surface user-friendly messages, not stack traces.
